videos.description: Amidst a 20-3 Cincinnati run against SMU, both teams trade impressive defensive stops before Gary Clark hits a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mustangs, Bearcats turn up the energy with wild sequence) 2018/01/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mustangs, Bearcats turn up the energy with wild sequence

videos.description: Bearcats guard Jarron Cumberland grabs the deflected ball and takes it down the court to feed a bounce pass to Jacob Evans for the off-balance and-1.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cincinnati capitalizes on SMU turnover) 2018/01/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincinnati capitalizes on SMU turnover

videos.description: Cincinnati guard Jarron Cumberland knocks down a long 3-pointer that extends the Bearcats' lead in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (3-pointer gives Cincinnati 17-point lead over SMU) 2018/01/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: 3-pointer gives Cincinnati 17-point lead over SMU

videos.description: No. 19 Cincinnati's Gary Clark and Jacob Evans carry the Bearcats with 18 points each and control the pace of the game through the end on a 76-56 win against SMU.
videos.headline: Bearcats hold SMU to a 20-point win
